## Disk & Memory Usage

Memory:
- RAM â†’ main memory
- Swap â†’ virtual memory from disk

Disk usage by filesystem:
df -hT

Folder size:
du -sh <folder-path>

All folder sizes:
du -sh *

Top 20 largest files/folders:
du -ah / | sort -rh | head -n 20

